#: ../../changelog.md:1
msgid "{material-regular}`history;1em` CHANGELOG"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:4
msgid ""
"Versions numbers are synchronised between [bot-"
"daemon](https://hub.docker.com/r/olvid/bot-daemon) docker image, [olvid-"
"bot](https://pypi.org/project/olvid-bot/) pypi module, and  [bot-python-"
"runner](https://hub.docker.com/r/olvid/bot-python-runner) docker image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:6
msgid ""
"Versions follow the MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH semantic. Every element is supposed"
" to be working with the others if sharing the same major and minor "
"versions, but it's recommended to always use the same patch version."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:9
msgid ""
"Minor versions will be incremented at least for every changes in [gRPC "
"API description](https://github.com/olvid-io/Olvid-Bot-Protobuf)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:12
msgid "Latest Release: Version 1.1.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:14
msgid "Added"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:16
msgid ""
"**location**: can now send location messages. Added MessageSendLocation "
"in protobuf, added `message location` command in {term}`CLI` and "
"message_send_location method in OlvidClient."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:17
msgid ""
"**daemon**: can now use TLS to encrypt communications between daemon and "
"bots."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:18
msgid "**olvid-bot**: added olvid.errors to easily catch specific api exceptions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:20
msgid "Changed"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:22
msgid ""
"**olvid-bot**: replaced DAEMON_HOSTNAME and DAEMON_PORT env variable by "
"DAEMON_TARGET."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:23
msgid ""
"**olvid-bot**: .client_key and .admin_client_key are now deprecated, use "
".env files instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:24
msgid ""
"**olvid-bot**: OlvidBot class is now deprecated, use OlvidClient instead "
"(they are equivalent)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:25
msgid ""
"**docker**: simplified and improved [bot-"
"daemon](https://hub.docker.com/r/olvid/bot-daemon) and [bot-python-"
"runner](https://hub.docker.com/r/olvid/bot-python-runner) image build "
"process. They are now faster to build and lighter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:27
msgid "Fixed"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:29
msgid ""
"**olvid-bot**: tools.SelfCleaningBot: clean_inbound_messages and "
"clean_outbound_messages parameters were not properly handled"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:33
msgid "Version 1.0.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:35
msgid "Initial release of Olvid Bots project."
msgstr ""

